<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Responsive Landing Page</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#f4f4f4;
}

header{
    background:#007BFF;
    color:white;
    padding:15px 50px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
}

header ul{
    list-style:none;
    display:flex;
}

header ul li{
    margin-left:20px;
}

header ul li a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.hero{
    height:90vh;
    background:linear-gradient(to right,#4facfe,#00f2fe);
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:50px;
}

.hero p{
    margin:20px 0;
    font-size:20px;
}

.btn{
    padding:12px 25px;
    background:white;
    color:#007BFF;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:5px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.features{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    gap:20px;
    padding:50px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    width:280px;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-10px);
}

.about{
    padding:50px;
    text-align:center;
}

.contact{
    background:white;
    padding:50px;
}

form{
    max-width:500px;
    margin:auto;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
}

input,textarea{
    margin:10px 0;
    padding:12px;
    font-size:16px;
}

button{
    padding:12px;
    background:#007BFF;
    color:white;
    border:none;
    cursor:pointer;
}

footer{
    background:#222;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

header{
    flex-direction:column;
}

header ul{
    margin-top:10px;
    flex-direction:column;
    text-align:center;
}

header ul li{
    margin:10px 0;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:35px;
}

.features{
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:center;
}

}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h2>Landing Page</h2>

<ul>
<li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
<li><a href="#">About</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
</ul>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<h1>Welcome to Our Website</h1>

<p>Create Beautiful Responsive Websites with HTML, CSS and JavaScript.</p>

<a href="#" class="btn">Get Started</a>

</section>

<section class="features">

<div class="card">
<h3>Responsive Design</h3>
<p>Works perfectly on desktop, tablet and mobile devices.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Fast Performance</h3>
<p>Lightweight design for better speed and user experience.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Easy Customization</h3>
<p>Modify colors, text and layout easily.</p>
</div>

</section>

<section class="about">

<h2>About Us</h2>

<p>
We build modern and responsive websites using HTML, CSS and JavaScript.
Our goal is to create attractive and user-friendly web applications.
</p>

</section>

<section class="contact">

<h2 align="center">Contact Us</h2>

<form id="contactForm">

<input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>

<input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>

<textarea rows="5" placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>

<button type="submit">Submit</button>

</form>

</section>

<footer>

<p>© 2026 Responsive Landing Page | All Rights Reserved</p>

</footer>

<script>
document.getElementById("contactForm").addEventListener("submit",function(e){
    e.preventDefault();
    alert("Thank you! Your message has been submitted.");
    this.reset();
});
</script>

</body>
</html>
